# ApkaSaathi — Complete Project Documentation

> **"ApkaSaathi"** (Hindi: आपका साथी = "Your Companion") — An AI-Powered Elderly Care Platform

---

## 1. Project Overview

**ApkaSaathi** is a **web-based elderly care platform** that uses **AI, electricity monitoring, and community networking** to ensure the safety, well-being, and companionship of elderly individuals living alone.

### Core Idea
Instead of using intrusive cameras or wearables, ApkaSaathi monitors **electricity consumption patterns** (e.g., lights, appliances, cooking) as a **proxy for daily activity detection**. If an elderly person's electricity usage deviates from their normal routine — say no kitchen usage at meal times — the system flags an **anomaly** and alerts family members.

### The 4 Pillars of ApkaSaathi

| Pillar | What It Does | Technology |
|---|---|---|
| **Smart Monitoring** | Tracks electricity usage to detect daily routines & anomalies | CSV data + Recharts + anomaly detection logic |
| **AI Companion** | Provides voice-based companionship & emotional support | ElevenLabs AI Voice + HeyGen Streaming Avatar |
| **Community Support** | Connects neighbours on a live map for mutual help | Leaflet.js map + Geolocation API |
| **Emergency SOS** | One-tap emergency alerts via phone calls + siren + location sharing | Twilio Voice API + Web Audio API + WhatsApp |

---

## 2. Problem Statement (Why This Project?)

India has **15 million+ elderly people living alone**. Key problems:

1. **Loneliness & Mental Decline** — Elderly living alone suffer from depression, cognitive decline, and lack of daily interaction.
2. **Remote Care Challenges** — Children living in different cities/countries struggle to know if their parents are safe, healthy, and following routines.
3. **Delayed Emergency Response** — Falls, health crises, or accidents often go undetected for hours because there's no immediate alert mechanism.

**Existing solutions** (cameras, wearable panic buttons) are **intrusive, expensive, and lack companionship**. ApkaSaathi solves all three problems in a **non-intrusive, privacy-focused, AI-driven** manner.

---

## 3. Technology Stack

| Technology | Purpose | Why We Chose It |
|---|---|---|
| **Next.js 16** | Full-stack React framework | Server-side rendering, API routes, file-based routing, optimal performance |
| **TypeScript** | Type-safe JavaScript | Catch bugs at compile-time, better developer experience |
| **Tailwind CSS 4** | Utility-first CSS framework | Rapid UI development, responsive design, consistent styling |
| **Framer Motion** | Animation library | Smooth, physics-based animations for better UX |
| **Recharts** | Data visualization library | Interactive charts for electricity usage graphs |
| **Leaflet.js + React-Leaflet** | Interactive maps | Lightweight, open-source mapping for community neighbour visualization |
| **ElevenLabs API** | AI voice synthesis & conversation | Natural-sounding voice for the AI companion (supports Hindi) |
| **HeyGen API** | Streaming video avatar | Lifelike animated avatar that lip-syncs with AI speech |
| **Twilio** | Phone call API | Automated emergency voice calls in Hindi |
| **Swiper.js** | Image slideshow/carousel | Smooth hero section image transitions |
| **Lucide React** | Icon library | Clean, consistent SVG icons throughout the app |
| **Web Audio API** | Browser-native audio | Emergency siren sound generation |
| **Geolocation API** | Browser-native location | Automatic user location for maps and emergency sharing |

