### 5.3 API Routes (Server-Side)

---

#### [api/sos/route.ts](file:///Users/janvigupta/Documents/Minor/apkasaathi/apkasaathi/app/api/sos/route.ts) — Emergency Call API
**What it does:** When SOS is triggered, this server-side route uses **Twilio** to make automated **voice calls in Hindi** to all emergency contacts simultaneously.

**Key concepts:**
- `twilio(accountSid, authToken)` — Initializes Twilio client
- **TwiML** — Twilio's XML markup for voice calls
- `Polly.Aditi` — Hindi-speaking AWS Polly voice
- `Promise.allSettled()` — Calls all contacts in parallel, handles partial failures gracefully
- The Hindi message: *"This is an emergency message from ApkaSaathi. Your family member needs immediate assistance. Please contact them now."*

---

#### [api/clone/route.ts](file:///Users/janvigupta/Documents/Minor/apkasaathi/apkasaathi/app/api/clone/route.ts) — Voice Cloning API
**What it does:** Takes a voice recording from a family member and creates a **cloned voice** using ElevenLabs, so the AI companion can speak in a familiar voice.

**Key concepts:**
- Receives audio as `FormData` (multipart upload)
- Sends it to `https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/voices/add`
- Returns a `voiceId` that can be used for text-to-speech in the cloned voice

---

#### [api/heygen/route.ts](file:///Users/janvigupta/Documents/Minor/apkasaathi/apkasaathi/app/api/heygen/route.ts) — Avatar Token API
**What it does:** Generates a streaming token from HeyGen for the video avatar feature.

