| 2 | **Electricity-Based Activity Recognition in Smart Homes** | Barsocchi et al., 2018 | Maps electricity patterns to daily activities (cooking, sleeping) | Springer |
| 3 | **Smart Home Monitoring for Elderly Care: A Systematic Review** | Peetoom et al., 2015 | Comprehensive review of monitoring technologies for elderly | Journal of Medical Internet Research |
| 4 | **AI Companions for Socially Isolated Older Adults** | Sidner et al., 2018 | Social robots and AI companions reducing loneliness | ACM Digital Library |
| 5 | **Anomaly Detection in IoT Systems: A Survey** | Cook et al., 2020 | Anomaly detection algorithms for sensor data patterns | IEEE |
| 6 | **ElevenLabs: Advancing Generative Voice AI** | ElevenLabs, 2024 | Text-to-speech and conversational AI for natural voice synthesis | ElevenLabs Blog / arXiv |
| 7 | **Community-Based Elderly Care: Technology-Mediated Social Support** | Chen & Schulz, 2016 | How technology bridges elderly with community | Gerontology Journal |
| 8 | **Real-Time Emergency Response Systems for Elderly: A Review** | Mubashir et al., 2013 | Emergency detection (falls, health crises) and response systems | Computer Vision and Image Understanding |
| 9 | **Privacy-Preserving Activity Recognition in Smart Homes** | Rashidi & Cook, 2009 | Non-camera-based monitoring that preserves privacy | IEEE Pervasive Computing |
| 10 | **Voice-Based Digital Assistants for Elderly Users** | Pradhan et al., 2020 | Design considerations for voice interfaces for older adults | CHI Conference |

